            </svg> 
           </picture> <h4 class="h-c-headline h-c-headline--four highlights-module__subhead">Do more with Google Cloud.</h4> <p class="highlights-module__description">You can use Google Marketing Platform together with Google Cloud to unlock advanced marketing use cases like building predictive models to get new insights to improve marketing performance.</p> <p> <a data-g-event="for enterprises" data-g-action="cloud" data-g-label="learn more" href="/about/resources/meeting-the-data-challenge-with-google-marketing-platform-and-google-cloud/" title="Learn more" class="h-c-link h-c-link--internal gmp-link">Learn more</a></p> </li> 
